---
import arrow from "../../assets/post/arrow.svg";
---

<section class="w-full px-6 grid grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-neutral-800">
    <h5 class="text-4xl">Overview</h5>
    <div class="col-span-3">
        <article class="space-y-6">
            <p>
                Mining has always been a complex and high-stakes industry,
                balancing the need for resource extraction with safety, cost
                efficiency, and environmental responsibility. In recent years,
                Geospatial Information Systems (GIS) have emerged as a
                transformative technology, giving mining companies the ability
                to visualize, analyze, and act on location-based data in ways
                that were once impossible.
            </p><p>
                By integrating spatial data with operational workflows, GIS
                empowers mining operations to work smarter, react faster, and
                plan with greater accuracyâ€”saving both lives and resources.
            </p>
        </article>
        <div class="w-full overflow-x-scroll mt-9">
            <div class="flex space-x-4 h-[36rem]">
                <img
                    src="/post/gallery-1.png"
                    alt=""
                    class="rounded-sm h-full"
                />
                <img
                    src="/post/gallery-2.png"
                    alt=""
                    class="rounded-sm h-full"
                />
                <img
                    src="/post/gallery-1.png"
                    alt=""
                    class="rounded-sm h-full"
                />
                <img
                    src="/post/gallery-2.png"
                    alt=""
                    class="rounded-sm h-full"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full flex justify-between items-center mt-6">
            <div class="space-x-3">
                {
                    [1, 2, 3, 4].map((i) => (
                        <button
                            class={
                                "cursor-pointer w-3 h-3 rounded-full " +
                                (i === 2 ? "bg-orange-800" : "bg-neutral-400")
                            }
                        />
                    ))
                }
            </div>
            <div class="flex space-x-3">
                <button
                    class="border border-neutral-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 cursor-pointer"
                >
                    <img src={arrow.src} />
                </button>
                <button
                    class="border border-neutral-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 cursor-pointer"
                    ><img src={arrow.src} class="rotate-180" />
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
